responses: {"Q0":"He is suffering from stage 2 Lymphoma and undergoing very difficult and challenging treatment. His friend is trying to raise some money to help him with the expenses."}

{"Q0":"How much if any sympathy one has for Jason and how much they are willing to give. I doubt I will win the drawing anyway. Of all the drawings I have been entered in I have never, ever won even one time.\n\nCancer runs in my family. My dad, brother, 2 uncles and one aunt have all died of cancer. I am sure I will too, it's not if but rather when."}

{"Q0":"My dad died of anaplastic thyroid cancer just 5 weeks from date of diagnosis. My brother died of renal cancer just 6 weeks from date of diagnosis. My grandmother died a horrible agonizing death from breast cancer.I could go on but enough."}
